Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========OP===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.79,0:00:16.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太过于坐立不安 你总是这么毛毛躁躁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:22.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要装做没有看见 我比任何人都更加爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:24.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你 喜欢你 喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:26.99,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你 喜欢你 喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:29.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你 喜欢你 喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:32.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你 喜欢你 喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:43.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪的星星让夜色更深沉 梦到的全都是你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:48.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使爱我 你也装得没有似的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:53.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你又在迷恋谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:01:04.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 男人们啊 心中总是牵挂着无数的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:14.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 到处都充满了玫瑰色 我心里实在好烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:20.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太过于坐立不安 你总是这么毛毛躁躁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:25.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要装做没有看见 我比任何人都更喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:28.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢你哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:36.59,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳的夏日约会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.98,0:01:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全国高校棒球暑期大赛的决战\N终于到了最后关头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九局下半 二人出局二垒有人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担任防守的大金井高校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投手是由主将布川来担任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一队正落后一分的P字学园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打击手是出名的强打鸟山队长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是转败为胜的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.29,0:02:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二好三坏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投手鸟山慢慢的进入投球位置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布川还没有投出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然没有投出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高高的举起来 终于将球投出了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键时刻开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打击出去 朝中间方向的打击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二垒的早川加开始全速的冲刺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游击手接到球快传本垒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟鹿死谁手呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出局 比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是惨垒 狂奔的早川哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和随后奔回本垒的鸟山互拥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二个人都以泪洗面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大金井高校的选手都哭成一团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一年来就是为了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有的青春都投注下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一份执着也就是高中生令人敬佩之处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:02:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么跟我的达令相差这么大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什么不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外形 兴趣 别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经认识半年多了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少应该跟我约会一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 外形的差别可以克服呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 神子的耐性也许会比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面的节目是青春心理学讲座
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的来宾是青春心理学学者伊藤老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.01,0:03:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈论男女交往的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 有关最近青年男女的交往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女交往的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在和从前并没有什么改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要认识了中意的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会产生所谓的心跳加快现象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有激烈而认真的热情与痴迷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭会咽到喉咙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上会失眠等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:04:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着便是进入打电话和写情书给对方的阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来便是约会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对着对方就会口干舌燥 双手会冒冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等生理现象都会表露无遗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般上不都是如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是男女交往的正常方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且 要是从来没有约会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能在一起的话简直无法想象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是真有其人 那就是不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的谈话是青春心理学者的伊藤老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个星期再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是倒霉 今天美女都不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的关系不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有按部就班来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令还是大吃大喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上睡得很舒服 还有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喉咙也不会口干舌燥 也没有汗流夹背
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我已经汗流夹背了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喉咙也已经口干舌燥了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这杯给我喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要跟达令约会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 我们约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 去约会嘛 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真啰嗦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说我跟你去约会也没有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我还没有跟你正式约会过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太自然吧…事到如今了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有约会过的夫妇才不自然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此也不能霸王硬上弓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要跟达令约会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 走嘛 去约会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟达令约会 去约会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 去约会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是来找我约会的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 这件事下次再商量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我是诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊代 改变心意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我闲得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟我约会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 去游泳吧 游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我追了半年多 总算对方有点回应了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 现在应该还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 别再做这些幼稚的举动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要跟我约会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不答应我就不还你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改天再跟你去 一定跟你去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要今天去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 你不答应的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把这本通讯录撕烂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业不借你抄 便当也不分给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 让我考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在还不死心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 求求你 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请跟我约会吧 就照你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有条件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一 把角藏起来 打扮成地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二 绝对不能使用超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三 除了上述之外\N约会时必须听从我的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂达令在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他的 一定是兴奋的初次约会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴奋的初次约会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在抵抗的话 又不知道她要搞什么花招了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是随便敷衍她一下算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是伊代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 想必就是她没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才真抱歉 现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在斜坡上的公共电话亭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问你是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当 我们去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里等你 赶快过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手脚倒是挺快的 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 这样打扮好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当 去约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好没有拒绝 竟然会这么正点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来看哦 有个可爱的女孩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女孩好正点啊 真想跟她要电话号码
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里 看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她应该有男朋友才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的男朋友想必来头不小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是安分点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 到底会是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 小姐面前太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道会是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 原来是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 太好了 跑来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太幸福了 这么可爱的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的确蛮不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 我们也去试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 到最高点去跳水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那个女孩的男朋友要从最高点跳水耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家仔细看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家上来让个位置给他们跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群混球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要谋杀我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 到底怎么了 男主角
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你腿软了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么正点的女朋友真是糟蹋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长相和胆量都应该是满分才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快让大家见识一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就让你们见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今只好硬着头皮干了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是小事一椿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高点不过比这里高一些吧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么急干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 怎么会这么高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉 拉姆 还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在看耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是算了的话 达令还算是男子汉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才不装模做样的话就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 根本就没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 赶快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 一起去吃饭吧 约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 水很容易导电
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你做得好事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令为什么会没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就习惯了 幸好我还很清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救护车 赶快打电话通知医生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪那些男人会如此兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 清凉的果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢达令 你真体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我帮你开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 你看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 在那边有个人坐在椅子上面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 长得蛮可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是在等男朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一样都是第一次约会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在一定口干舌燥 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么样的男朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 因为突然从后面冲出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点小事不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 卷发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 阿当 你跑来这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆小姐 怎么打扮成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻飘飘的秀发加上迷人的背心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贴身的短裤再加上可爱的口袋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当 从实招来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…有许多的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟达令在约会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我第一次跟达令约会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷发 过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 阿当
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是正在跟那个女孩约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我盼望以久的初次约会 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冷静而客观的判断之下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆换成美纪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美纪换成拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆换成美纪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美纪换成拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来即使我选择了美纪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果仍然是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来还是会选择拉姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不能欺骗自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 这都是上天在作弄我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你是拉姆亲卫队的队员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以跟别的女孩子约会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两件事毫无关联
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.91,0:16:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一个健康的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是眼镜他是怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当 难道你要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子 谁说我要去告密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑去取悦眼镜 对我而言也没有任何好处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不可貌相 你竟然还有女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 丑陋方面我怎么比得上你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你何必这么客气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 骨骼的结构就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这应该是老早就注定的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 我认输了 真的认输了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么 赶快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你们在聊什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当 你们待会有什么计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们一起行动如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言为定 二对一起去约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像玩任何东西都很内行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你不是想在拉姆面前表现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最拿手的轮鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你真的是见识不足
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 一起溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不太方便
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管我 你自己去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能教我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.87,0:17:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 约会时讲好了听我的指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听清楚 不要跑太远哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实阿当跟拉姆是夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫妇？夫妇为什么是第一次约会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们之间是无法用常理说明的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 小姐 好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们一起溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拉姆 不准跟别的男人搭讪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道有家牛肉饭蛮不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.03,0:18:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快抓紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来我根本就不必别人操心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以达令才不来陪我啊 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:18:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要莫名其妙的突然靠过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 达令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好惨的声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 达令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？令人羡慕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令的手心出汗了 好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 阿当这个家伙还真会表演
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在众人面前敢做这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很像一对夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我要请客哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令还痛不痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 在这里用餐是有规矩的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就跟那个女孩做 明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定好了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一客汉堡牛排饭 美纪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你一样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是那个 拉姆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 不要这样 住手 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是规矩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…能不能再点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服务生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我烤鱼片和香蕉果汁加布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再给我综合比萨和生菜沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上炸虾咖理和冰淇淋汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个没水准的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 达令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 叫你模仿她是我的不对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天很开心 能够跟达令约会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的那么开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天谢谢你跟我约会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很开心 事先讲好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你要去哪里 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次约会一起回家的话很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.14,0:22:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在想什么 那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么一点精神也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆那个家伙 就光会作弄人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.54,0:22:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实今天又何必回幽浮去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来就来说走就走 到底把我当成什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹够了就快回来 拉姆大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 达令你好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再约会二、三次之前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.84,0:23:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是暂时住在这里吧 好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.18,0:23:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========预告===========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.66,0:23:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在海边耶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃西瓜就会遭惩罚的村子里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.15,0:23:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于西瓜而引起了一场大混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.25,0:23:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才刚平静了一下子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.85,0:24:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然被爱哭的感伤妖怪所纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.10,0:24:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 夏天的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.97,0:24:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
